=== Noun ===
'''button'''

# A [[fastener]] consisting of a knob that is passed through a slit in the adjacent material.
# A mechanical device meant to be pressed with a finger in order to open or close an electric circuit or to activate a mechanism.
## A software item which can be selected as an activator of an attatched function.
# A badge worn on clothes, fixed with a [[pin]] through the fabric.

